➜听说有人过节花出了“过年”的感觉？
http://www.sohu.com/a/423706143_99910418	29905
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><span><span>各位谈宝宝们：</span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><span><span>大家好！</span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>今天谈谈想跟大家聊聊</span><strong><span><span>【</span>十一账单】 </span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201010/16e6d348b7f541e7839ae24982cb52ec.jpeg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><span><span>经文旅部数据中心测算</span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><span><span>八天长假期间</span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><span>全国共接待国内游客6.37亿人次</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><span>实现国内旅游收入4665.6亿元</span></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201010/aa6739977f88417b84033b0b808a79f4.gif" /></p>
<p><span>2020年“十一”黄金周结束</span></p>
<p><span>部分网友也陆续晒出自己的账单</span></p>
<p><span>有人说</span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
